
                   DAZ SON OF MORSECODE PRESENTS:-

                      A SOLUTION OF NOVAGEN's

                           MERCENARY III


 A QUICK AND EASY SOLUTION
 =========================

 BEFORE TRYING TO COMPLETE GAME TRY TO BECOME AWARE OF YOUR SURROUNDING IN THE
 THE GAME.

 HERE GOES NOTHING:

 WHEN THE DOOR OPEN IN THE PRISON INITIATE THE RUNNING MODE.
 THEN GOTO THE REAR OF THE PRISON AND GET KEYS AND BOARD EAGLE.  
 FLY TO CO-ORDS 00-06 (DOOBERRY'S SOLICITORS / METIS).
 LEAVE EAGLE AND DROP KEY.
 GOTO FLOOR 9 AND USE THE TRANSPORTER TO TRANSPORTER TO NO 2 TRANSPORTER.
 YOU WILL NOW BE AT 08-03 (ETA HOUSE / ERIS).
 GOTO FLOOR 9 AND GET THE A-Z COMPUTER AND GOTO GROUND FLOOR AND LEAVE.
 GET THE BUS NO. 29 TRAVELLING LEFT TO RIGHT ON LEAVING BUILDING.
 USE BUS PASS IN INVENTORY. LEAVE BUS AT MAGARET'S REREAT (06-03).
 FIND KEY E IN HER RETREAT AND GO AND BOARD SAME BUS GOING IN THE SAME 
 DIRECTION.
 LEAVE THE BUS AT BARGAIN TRADERS (12-03).
 ENTER AND BUY THE KEY TO THE TWIN TURBO (TT).
 LEAVE SHOP AND BOARD THE TT AND TURN ON A-Z COMPUTER.
 NOW FLY TO LOCATION 09-02 (PLAY TESTER STORES).
 GOTO BASEMENT AND COLLECT SHIELD, SIGHTS AND RED BEACON DETECTOR.
 LEAVE AND BOARD TT. FLY TO CO-ORDS 03-04 SNOW ISLAND/ERIS.
 GET THE POWER GLOVE FROM SHOP.
 DROP TAXI AND BUS CARD JUST INSIDE SHOP.(REMB WHERE YOU PUT THEM).
 FLY TO ETA HOUSE, CAPITAL CITY/ERIS (08-03).
 GET TT AND GOTO FLOOR 1 AND TELEPORT TO VESTA (TEL NO 4).
 LEAVE VESTA PARLIAMENT BUILDING AND DROP & BOARD TT.
 FLY TO CO-ORDS 05-04 (ELECTION REGISTRAR).
 ENTER AND GOTO FLOOR 1.
 GET COMPUTER AND TYPE   MERCENARY   INTO COMPUTER AND DROP COMPUTER.
 BOARD TT AND FLY OFF PLANET.
 LOCATE DAMOCLES (WHITE LINES) AND FLY TO DAMOCLES.
 ONCE ON DAMOCLES, LOCATE THE WHITE FLASHING BEACON AND FLY TO IT.
 ONCE LANDED, LEAVE TT AND PICKUP PULVIN ORE.
 PAT YOURSELF ON THE BACK, CONGRATZ ALL ROUND!!!
 WELLDONE PRESIDENT MERCENARY!!!
 THIS IS ONLY ONE SOLUTION.
 THERE ARE MORE SO LOOK AROUND (EG DESTROY ALL OF PC BILS SHIPS) .      


 P.S. IF YOU FIND LOCATION OF AND
 KEYS OTHER THAN B C E AND THE KEYS
 LOCATED AT BQ LOCKSMITHS THEN DROP
 A LINE TO MORSECODE OF LSD.

 SON OF MORSECODE FOR LSD ON 17/1/91

